        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2007-12-27T16:32:37Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Child Care Affordability Act of 2007 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) allow a tax deduction for expenses paid for household and dependent care services necessary for gainful employment; (2) increase the dollar limitation on the tax credit for such expenses; (3) provide for an inflation adjustment after 2008 to the dollar amounts for such tax deduction and tax credit; and (4) make such tax credit refundable. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
